description:
Available 1/1/25. Ideally located in the heart of Fort Point, within the Seaport District, on the corner of Melcher Street and A street. With 14ft ceiling heights, factory sized windows and new appliances, including in-unit w/d. It can be rented furnished. This location is a short distance from the Seaport, South Boston, South End, Financial District, South Station (red line to Cambridge), access to the highway and a quick drive to the airport. Some of the best restaurants Boston has to offer are seconds/minutes from your front door. Trader Joe's, Whole Foods and Roche Brothers within close proximity. Come enjoy this stylish and convenient lifestyle! The home boasts polished chrome fixtures, granite countertops to create a distinctive, contemporary urban feel. Live in Boston's trendiest and most dynamic neighborhood! To get above it all, a common Roof Deck is available to all residents. The apt can be rented furnisched and unfurnished, minimum 3 months to 12 months.

Fully furnished apt, it can be rented from 5 months to 12 months unfurnished or furnished.
